data.title: The Hansbrough brothers: no man left behind
data.meta_description: We all knew putting the Hansbrough brothers on the same NBA team would be a great idea.
data.text:
Tyler Hansbrough is an incumbent disappointing lottery pick for the Indiana Pacers. Ben Hansbrough is a fringe NBA player picked up by the Pacers due to injuries. Ben and Tyler were on the court together Wednesday night when Cavaliers big man Tristan Thompson hit Psycho B in the head with an elbow during a loose ball battle. And then we realized letting Psycho T play with his brother was a bad idea, as evidenced in the video above.

I will now withdraw my standing request that the Clippers sign Taylor Griffin.
